extends layout

block content
  .box-container
    .header-section
      h1.privacy-title Privacy Policy
      p.privacy-subtitle Learn how we collect and use your personal information.

    .content-section
      h2.section-title Information We Collect
      p
        | We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and payment information when you register or make purchases.

      h2.section-title How We Use Your Information
      p
        | The information collected helps us process transactions, provide customer support, and improve our services. We may also use the information to communicate with you regarding updates and promotional offers.

      h2.section-title Sharing of Information
      p
        | We do not sell or trade your personal information to third parties. However, we may share data with service providers to fulfill our business operations, such as payment processing and customer support.

      h2.section-title Data Security
      p
        | We employ measures to secure your personal information against unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the internet is entirely secure.

      h2.section-title Your Rights
      p
        | You have the right to access, update, or request the deletion of your personal data. Please contact our customer support if you have any concerns about your privacy rights.

      h2.section-title Changes to This Policy
      p
        | We may update this policy periodically. We encourage you to review it regularly to stay informed about how we protect your information.

    .d-flex.justify-content-center
      a(href='/')
        button Back to Home
